<main>
    <section class="events">
        <h2>Memberships and Guest Policies</h2>

        <div class="membership-info">
            <h3>Facility Memberships</h3>
            <p>All current Brandeis students, faculty, and staff may use the athletic facilities free of charge. A valid Brandeis ID card must be presented to enter and upon request.</p>
            <h3>Membership Policy</h3>
            <p>Facility memberships can be purchased by eligible individuals by submitting a membership application. Once information is verified and membership application approved, instructions will be sent for picking up membership cards. Please contact Tom Rand (rand@brandeis.edu) or Michael Matt (mmatt@brandeis.edu) with any questions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="membership-types">
            <h3>Type of Memberships</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Alumni</li>
                <li>Immediate Family of current student, faculty or staff (must be 18 years or older)</li>
                <li>Waltham Senior Citizen (must be 65 years or older and a Waltham resident)</li>
                <li>Current BOLLI student</li>
            </ul>
            <h3>Pricing</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>$500/full year</li>
                <li>$300/semester</li>
                <li>$250/summer</li>
                <li>$100/intersession break</li>
            </ul>
            <p>All payments are due in full at the start of the membership period. No refunds. Credit card, cash, and check payments accepted.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="guest-policy">
            <h3>Guest Policy</h3>
            <p>Current Brandeis students, faculty, staff, and members may bring guests into the facility.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>All guests must be accompanied by their Brandeis sponsor at all times.</li>
                <li>All guests must sign a waiver of liability and assumption of risk form at the front desk.</li>
                <li>All guests must pay a fee of $10/guest per day. No appointment is necessary. Cash, checks, and credit cards accepted.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="child-policy">
            <h3>Child Policy</h3>
            <p>Current Brandeis students, faculty, staff, and members may bring their children into the facility.</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Children 12 years and younger - no charge</li>
                <li>Children 13 years and older must follow the Guest Policy (see above).</li>
                <li>Children must be supervised by their parent/guardian at all times in the facility.</li>
                <li>Children 12 years and younger are NOT allowed in the weight room.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

